The Desert Dwarves live in a small settlement in the deserts of Souvrael.
The Dwarves live in a peaceful, just society, generally unaffected by
outside influences. Physically, they are a short, hardy race. In addition
to an innate resistance to magic and psionics, they tend to be quite
healthy and strong, but suffer somewhat from a stubbiness in their limbs.
Despite their strength, their small size often also creates difficulties
in wielding larger weapons.
